5 - PRE-DEPLOYMENT ACTIONS:
---------------------------
No action needs to be performed before the deployment

6 - DEPLOYMENT RECIPE:
----------------------
sudo yum clean all
sudo yum remove xt
sudo yum install xt

7 - POST-DEPLOYMENT ACTIONS:
----------------------------
Run following script on DC1 and DC3 only,
cd /tmp
sudo -u xt-web /opt/xt/xt-perl/bin/perl -I/opt/xt/deploy/xtracker/lib /opt/xt/deploy/xtracker/script/housekeeping/push_restrictions.pl

8 - ROLLBACK PLAN:
------------------
sudo yum downgrade xt


